Enum DirectoryIdentifier

    public enum DirectoryIdentifier
extends java.lang.Enum<DirectoryIdentifier>
    This program enumerates Image File Directory (IFD) types typically found within TIFF image files.

      • getNextDirectoryType

        public static DirectoryIdentifier getNextDirectoryType(DirectoryIdentifier dirType)
        Finds the next available IFD structure from the current directory. For instance, going from IFD0 to IFD1. At the time of its development, it only supports up to IFD3 maximum.
        Parameters:
        dirType - the type of directory being read
        Returns:
        the next available DirectoryIdentifier, or the current DirectoryIdentifier if the maximum IFD number has been reached
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the input value is TIFF_DIRECTORY_IFD3, which is the maximum
